*Brak* je ukupnost odnosa između muškarca i žene. (Marriage is the relationship between a man and a woman.)

*Braka* se često čine iz ljubavi. (Marriages are often made out of love.)

Mnogi ljudi se ne žele *brakati*. (Many people don’t want to get married.)

Oni koji se *brakaju* često žive srećno i dugo. (Those who get married often live happily and long.)

Mnogi parovi se odlučuju za *brak*. (Many couples decide to get married.)

*Brakovi* se često obnavljaju. (Marriages are often renewed.)